  "body": "Introduced by https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/pull/15204 cc @alwx \r\n\r\nCausing pinned messages e2e tests to fail. \r\n\r\n**Steps:** \r\n\r\n1. Open any chat\r\n2. Send some messages\r\n3. Pin a message to generate pinned list\r\n4. Scroll to the top of chat history \r\n5. See if pinned list button is availabe\r\n\r\n**Actual result:** pinned list button is not shown. Unable to open pinned list as pinned list bar disappears when user located at the top of chat history. \r\n\r\n**Expected result:** pinned list button is displed as per design\r\n\r\nhttps://www.figma.com/file/7KIYbhoqNGAIFonE0w9TDz/Messages-for-Mobile?type=design&node-id=7950-519665&t=XaUGsCIHDWIbcWct-0\r\n\r\n<img width=\"313\" alt=\"Messages for Mobile â€“ Figma 2023-06-02 11-59-38\" src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/97245802/019d8632-8db9-41de-bc1a-d500905fe78b\">\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: nightly \r\n- Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
